Subject: [PATCH 18/26] doc: imagemap: document on-demand loading framework

Describe the imagemap framework architecture: the translation table
that tracks mapped regions, the three storage backends (block, MTD,
UBI), the IMAGEMAP_BACKEND() linker-list registration mechanism,
and the integration with bootm for on-demand FIT sub-image loading.

Signed-off-by: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
